; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">varia=
nt of concern</a>, referred to as =E2=80=9Comicron.=E2=80=9D Let=E2=80=99s =
say you predict that omicron will be a really big deal, and you would like =
to make a bet on that prediction. There are various=C2=A0ways to implement =
that bet using regular financial assets =E2=80=94=C2=A0buy mask manufacture=
rs or short cruise lines or whatever =E2=80=94=C2=A0but they each involve r=
