=9D Create a new crypto token on some blockchain. =E2=80=9COnly 10,000 of t=
his Omicron Coin will ever be minted,=E2=80=9D or whatever. Now you have a =
scarce version of the word omicron, and you can start ascribing value to it=
. The more people say =E2=80=9Comicron,=E2=80=9D the more people will look =
to buy Omicron Coin, and the more valuable it will be.</p><p style=3D"margi=
